      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "凌风公子",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "风云雷鸣",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "呼！呼！呼！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "砰！砰！砰！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "砰！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "白云苍狗，沧海桑田",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "人生如梦",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "海外三煞",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "啊！白哥！你醒转来啦！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你那是在荒岛上没有人的地方，到了中原，处处有人，就不能不穿衣服……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哎……你真美…",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "豹突山庄",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "什么好东西？现在给我看不是一样吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 314
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不多不少，整整六十天。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 336,
      "line_end": 336
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "怎么？我在这地方昏迷了两个月啦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 338,
      "line_end": 338
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "两个多月了！你忘记来时是冬天，现在已经到了春天。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 340,
      "line_end": 340
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "白哥哥，你到哪里去？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 354,
      "line_end": 354
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "去找四大豪门为父亲报仇。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 356,
      "line_end": 356
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "白哥哥，你不用去报仇了。四大豪门均已星散，'青蚨神'金九，'乾坤掌'云宗龙，'混元指'司空晋，'摘星手'慕容涵，以及'霸王鞭'樊非均已被人杀死了……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 358,
      "line_end": 358
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "翠翠，你这岂不是信口胡说？他们四大豪门势可盖天，个个门下高手如云，怎么会一时之间被人杀死……",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 360,
      "line_end": 360
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那么，武林四公子呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 370,
      "line_end": 370
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "武林四公子，现在不过是局促一隅的一个小头目罢了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 372,
      "line_end": 372
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "展白想了想，果然在武林中从未听到此名号，不由纳罕道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 380,
      "line_end": 380
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那白衣银扇书生又是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 388,
      "line_end": 388
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "此处是什么地方……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 404,
      "line_end": 404
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "天仙魔女",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 452,
      "line_end": 452
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这有什么好看？我已经看过很多次了……",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 454,
      "line_end": 454
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "翠妹，你是一个圣洁的少女，今后我不希望你再做出如此丑恶……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 468,
      "line_end": 468
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "天仙魔女",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 474,
      "line_end": 474
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "白哥哥！你知道我的师父是谁吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 480,
      "line_end": 480
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "妹妹没跟我说过，我怎会知道？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 482,
      "line_end": 482
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我的师父就是'天仙魔女'。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 484,
      "line_end": 484
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那……不可能吧？'天仙魔女'据今已有二百余年，她怎能活到现在……",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 486,
      "line_end": 486
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这画像本是我师父修炼的一种特殊武功，名为'姹女迷魂大法'，据说厉害无比，不论武功多么高强之士，也难以抵挡，就是修炼至心如槁木死灰的道行高僧，也无法与之抗衡……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 496,
      "line_end": 496
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只眼郎君",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 498,
      "line_end": 498
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "而且，也不正当。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 500,
      "line_end": 500
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这实在大有分别：譬如一个人要到某一个地方，放正路不走，而走人歧途，虽然开始所差无几，但却是差之毫厘，谬之千里……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 508,
      "line_end": 508
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但他的话尚未说完，翠翠已娇嗔道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 526,
      "line_end": 526
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这回算你聪明，这天佛录上隐藏的三门奇功，不但一定要二人合练，而且还非要跟妹妹合练不可，不是妹夸口，天下虽大，但除了妹妹一人，不做第二人想……同时……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 550,
      "line_end": 550
    }
  ],
